The company has emerged to be one of the large online taxi service provider reaching out to the riders from continents across the globe. Our mission is to make taxi rides hassle free, convenient, secured and reliable from every mode of communication. We keep our taxi booking services high on technology with standards that are internationally implemented and can be matched against the best in industry in terms of comfort, reliability and trust. Our Mobile apps for drivers and passengers makes every trip automated with few easy taps. Our dispatch team works on 24X7 concept which means ample phone support to the passenger. So next time you need a taxi to airport or you need head home safe after an awesome Saturday night, or you're just planning a weekend road trip with your friends or any other reason, trust us to help you with the right taxi at right time!

string.name: default_privacy_policy
string.p: Your privacy is very important to us. Accordingly, The following outlines our privacy policy.

ul.li: Before or at the time of collecting personal information, we will identify the purposes for which information is being collected.

We will collect and use of personal information solely with the objective of fulfilling those purposes specified by us and for other compatible purposes, unless we obtain the consent of the individual concerned or as required by law.
We will only retain personal information as long as necessary for the fulfillment of those purposes.
We will collect personal information by lawful and fair means and, where appropriate, with the knowledge or consent of the individual concerned.
Personal data should be relevant to the purposes for which it is to be used, and, to the extent necessary for those purposes, should be accurate, complete, and up-to-date.
We will protect personal information by reasonable security safeguards against loss or theft, as well as unauthorized access, disclosure, copying, use or modification.
We will make readily available to customers information about our policies and practices relating to the management of personal information.

string.p: We are committed to conducting our business in accordance with these principles in order to ensure that the confidentiality of personal information is protected and maintained.
